						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up on the bank of a tank.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīra-pāṇḍya year 5: 1221 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription can be assigned to about the 13th Century A.D. on grounds of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It records an order issued by Añjādaperumāḷ Porkaiyaṉ Chēdirāyaṉ for desilting the tank from out of the income from tax called <hi rend="italic">pāśippāṭṭam</hi> collected from Periyakuḷam in Rājachūḍāmaṇich-chaturvēdimaṅgalam. </p>						

						</summary>
